  "details": "Avahi is a system which facilitates service discovery on a local network via the mDNS/DNS-SD protocol suite. This enables you to plug your laptop or computer into a network and instantly be able to view other people who you can chat with, find printers to print to or find files being shared.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nAvahi 0.8 allows a local denial of service (NULL pointer dereference and daemon crash) against avahi-daemon via the D-Bus interface or a &quot;ping .local&quot; command.(CVE-2021-36217)",
